{
  "name": "RPlog_A_Fateful_Return",
  "title": "A Fateful Return",
  "summary": "On a fine day in the Belleau-a-Lir district of New Alderaan, the pilot and mercenary Kalna shares a casual meal with the older operator Gustaf Heram, who gently chides her table manners and reminisces about his son Baral and his late wife. Kalna offers her piloting skills for an upcoming operation, and the two travel to the Vandelhelm system, where she threads a treacherous asteroid field with heroic skill that leaves Gustaf both alarmed and impressed. Aboard ship they swap personal history -- Kalna reveals her connection to swoop racing and an independent pilot the Empire took a dark interest in -- before meeting Gustaf's associate Baral and surveying their objectives. Gustaf lays out the plan: a multi-pronged raid on guarded depots, aided by his second-in-command who has feigned betrayal to embed himself among the enemy. Kalna, eager and brimming with confidence, presses for details on the roughly twenty-five to thirty defenders they will face with a force of fifteen across three fronts as the operation takes shape.",
